    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/4d1e65c8dfd6492d387160d5b910a3ca.poster.avif?t=1676445597\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/4d1e65c8dfd6492d387160d5b910a3ca.webm?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/4d1e65c8dfd6492d387160d5b910a3ca.mp4?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enter The Labyrinth is a single player action rpg that takes place in a world abandoned by its god during an apocalyptic event, a never ending rainstorm that eventually flooded the planet, forcing survivors to sail the oceans searching for a rumored last piece of land, a mysterious island, where an ancient Labyrinth exists, leading survivor's to a new world called Paradise. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/858bc1769713b5609a5ed136b41409db.poster.avif?t=1676445597\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/858bc1769713b5609a5ed136b41409db.webm?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/858bc1769713b5609a5ed136b41409db.mp4?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The intense gameplay focuses on weapon based combat using classic elements like swords and shields but with a heavy emphasis on weapon colliding, armor breaking, and cutting of flesh. Weapons have weight and with this consideration, when you swing, matters. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/d38708cd1d848b2f1652e6e3e17bbf14.poster.avif?t=1676445597\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/d38708cd1d848b2f1652e6e3e17bbf14.webm?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/d38708cd1d848b2f1652e6e3e17bbf14.mp4?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the island, outside and within the dungeon for valuable loot, mighty weapons and armors. Face demons and fight warriors in battles that all feel like boss battles. Every battle matters. Every attack matters. Navigating through the Labyrinth will involve some metroidvanian exploration aspects. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/b1b4970f366019ac854edecd5eb1b3a7.poster.avif?t=1676445597\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/b1b4970f366019ac854edecd5eb1b3a7.webm?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/b1b4970f366019ac854edecd5eb1b3a7.mp4?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Directional attacks allow you to specifically target where to attack. Exposing weak points to make kills easier. Or swing against an attack to parry and defend.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/65e0d51ffe1128ef58f5acce74b95a03.poster.avif?t=1676445597\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/65e0d51ffe1128ef58f5acce74b95a03.webm?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/65e0d51ffe1128ef58f5acce74b95a03.mp4?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you explore the Labyrinth and The Island, you'll find unique weapons and powerful armours which matter. A single strike to the head can be the end for the hero, so equipping helmets for example, are the difference between life and death when you do get caught with a strike. A natural approach to difficulty. This wont be a simple, easy , Journey....<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/c3357b2aa65c64d1da9a14ef1cf7bd5f.poster.avif?t=1676445597\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/c3357b2aa65c64d1da9a14ef1cf7bd5f.webm?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878930/extras/c3357b2aa65c64d1da9a14ef1cf7bd5f.mp4?t=1676445597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Now in development. Help support the project by wishlisting and following the development updates on twitter.",
